      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Darbôs Sa-eeschanas Telti: Ta\nDshwofta Galdt / un winna\naifschanjamas Kahrtis/ un win-\nna Stabbi/ un winna Kahjas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lihds ar ta Pagalma\nStabbeem apfahrt / un winnu\nRahjahm / un winnu Naglehem/\nun winnu Wirwehm/ ar wiſſeem\nwinnu Rihkeem/ pehz wiſſu win-\nna Darbu; un jums buhs tohs\nfargajamus Rihkus/ kas winnu\nNastasbuhs/ teem ar Wahrdeem\ncesfaitiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schi laid irr ta Kalpo-\nfchana to Merata Dehlu Rad-\ndo/ wiſſôs winnu Darbôs/ eeksch\ntahs Sa-eeschanas Telts / ap-\nvafsch Jhtamara / Aâroza ta\nPreestera Dehta Rohkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad Mohsus un Aârons/\nun tahs Draudses Wirfneeki /\nſkaitija tohs Kaätitern Dehns/\npehz winnu Raddeem / un pehz\nwinnu Tehwu Namina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Trihsdesmits Gaddus\nwezzus un pahri / lihds tam peez-\ndefinitiam Gaddam/ wiſſi / kas Karrâ\neet warreja / ka tee dar-\nbotohs pee tahs Sa-eeschanas\nTelts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad bija winnu Pulki/\npehz faaweemRaddeem/diwi tuhk-\nſtochi/ ſechtsimts un peezdes-\nmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee irr to Kaätitero\nRaddu Pulki/ wiſſi/ kas pee Sa-\neeschanas Telts darbojahs / fo\nMohsus un Aârons bija ſkaiti-\njuschi/ us ta KUNGA Wahrdü/\nur Mohsu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta lihds arridsan tee Ger-\nſona Dehlu Pulki/ pehz faaweem\nRaddeem/ un pehz faawo Tehwu\nNamma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Trihsdesmits Gaddus\nwezzi un pahri / lihds tam peez-\ndefinitiam Gaddam / wiſſi / kas\nKarrâ eet warreja/ ka tee darbo-\ntohs eeksch tahs Sa-eeschanas\nTelts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winnu Pulki bija pehz\nfaaweem Raddeem pehz faawu\nTehwu Namma / diwi tuhksto-\nſchi/ ſechtsimts un trihsdefimits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee irr tee Pulki / no-\nteem Gersona Dehlu Raddeem/\nwiſſi / kas Sa-eeschanas Telti\ndarbojahs/ fo Mohsus un Aâ-\nrons lihdsinaja / pehz ta KUN-\nGA Pawehlefchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Pulki to Merata\nDehlu Raddu/ pehz faaweemRad-\ndeem pehz faawu Tehwu Namna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Trihsdesmits Gaddus\nwezzi un pahri / lihds peezdefini-\ntam Gaddam/ wiſſi / kas Karrâ\neet warreja / ka tee darbotohs\neeksch tahs Sa-eeschanas Telts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winnu Pulki bija pehz\nwinnu Raddeem trihs tuhksto-\nſchi diwisimts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee irr tee Merata\nDehlo Raddu Pulki/ fo Mohsus\nun Aârons irr ſkaitijſchi/ pehz ta\nKUNGA Pawehlefchanas zaar\nMohsu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi tee Pulki/ fo Moh-\nsus/ un Aârons/ un tee Israëla\nWirfneeki irr ſkaitijſchi / no-\nteem Lewiteem/ pehz winnu Rad-\ndeem/\n"
    }
  ],
